## Key Findings

## Sales Funnel
- Only 31% of users who view products add items to cart.
- Payment-to-purchase conversion rate exceeds 90%.

## Traffic Sources
- Social media drives high traffic but lower conversions.
- Email marketing generates stronger conversion rates.

## Customer Journey
- Average purchase journey takes approximately 25 minutes.

## Recommendations
- Improve product page UX to increase cart additions.
- Increase investment in email marketing campaigns.
- Continue monitoring checkout performance.
